INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("139", "1", "2016-03-19 21:03:20", "2016-03-19 21:03:20", "[et_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"on\" specialty=\"off\"][et_pb_fullwidth_slider admin_label=\"Fullwidth Slider\" show_arrows=\"on\" show_pagination=\"on\" auto=\"off\" auto_ignore_hover=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" remove_inner_shadow=\"off\" background_position=\"default\" background_size=\"default\" hide_content_on_mobile=\"off\" hide_cta_on_mobile=\"off\" show_image_video_mobile=\"off\" custom_button=\"off\" button_letter_spacing=\"0\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\"]\r\n\r\n[et_pb_slide button_text=\"Apply\" button_link=\"#\" background_image=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/mainCover-3.jpg\" background_position=\"default\" background_size=\"default\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" use_bg_overlay=\"on\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" alignment=\"center\" background_layout=\"dark\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" text_border_radius=\"3\" header_font_select=\"default\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_font_select=\"default\" button_font=\"||||\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" heading=\"The Autonomous University of Social Movements\"]\r\n\r\nThe Autonomous University of Social Movements (AUSM) is an alternative educational program focused on the study of social movements in Mexico, socialism in Cuba, and community organizing in Chicago. AUSM combines rigorous theoretical study, participatory action research, and experiential learning with powerful social actors struggling for justice, autonomy, and democracy.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide button_text=\"More info\" button_link=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/mexico-study-abroad/\" background_image=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/stone-wall.jpg\" background_position=\"default\" background_size=\"default\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"off\" alignment=\"center\" background_layout=\"dark\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" text_border_radius=\"3\" header_font_select=\"default\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_font_select=\"default\" button_font=\"||||\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" heading=\"Study Abroad in Mexico\"]\r\n\r\nThe Study Abroad Program offers university students the opportunity to study Mexico’s most important living social movements.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide button_text=\"More info\" button_link=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/cuba-study-abroad/\" background_image=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/che.jpg\" background_position=\"default\" background_size=\"default\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"on\" alignment=\"center\" background_layout=\"dark\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" text_border_radius=\"3\" header_font_select=\"default\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_font_select=\"default\" button_font=\"||||\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" heading=\"Study Abroad in Cuba\"]\r\n\r\nYou will encounter a reality in Cuba unlike anything you have experienced. Study the history, culture, and politics of Cuba\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_slide][et_pb_slide button_text=\"More info\" button_link=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/cuba-study-abroad/\" background_image=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/mil-park-chi-town.jpg\" background_position=\"default\" background_size=\"default\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" use_bg_overlay=\"off\" use_text_overlay=\"on\" alignment=\"center\" background_layout=\"light\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" text_border_radius=\"3\" header_font_select=\"default\" header_font=\"||||\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_font_select=\"default\" button_font=\"||||\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" heading=\"ASUM Graduate Program\"]\r\n\r\nYou will encounter a reality in Cuba unlike anything you have experienced. Study the history, culture, and politics of Cuba\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_slide]\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_fullwidth_slider][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section admin_label=\"section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\"][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Study Abroad Mexico\" url_new_window=\"off\" animation=\"top\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%165%%\" icon_color=\"#a8a8a8\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle_border=\"on\" circle_border_color=\"#e0e0e0\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" url=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/mexico-study-abroad/\"]\r\n\r\nFocus on the theory, practice and context of the Zapatista movement.  Program features study and living in a Zapatista cultural/political center.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Study Abroad Cuba\" url_new_window=\"off\" animation=\"top\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%165%%\" icon_color=\"#a8a8a8\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle_border=\"on\" circle_border_color=\"#e0e0e0\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" url=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/cuba-study-abroad/\"]\r\n\r\nFocus on the history, culture and politics of Cuba, with a constructively critical look at the Cuban revolution.  Program features home stays in Havana, travel to provinces, and experiential learning.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Graduate Program\" url_new_window=\"off\" animation=\"top\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%366%%\" icon_color=\"#a8a8a8\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle_border=\"on\" circle_border_color=\"#e0e0e0\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" url=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/masters-in-community-organizing/\"]\r\n\r\nStudy the theory and practice of community organizing in the US context.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Speaking Tours\" url_new_window=\"off\" animation=\"top\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%149%%\" icon_color=\"#a8a8a8\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle_border=\"on\" circle_border_color=\"#e0e0e0\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\nDivi will change the way you build websites forever. The advanced page builder makes it possible to build truly dynamic pages without learning code.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_cta admin_label=\"Call To Action\" title=\"Contact Us\" button_url=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/contact-us-3/\" button_text=\"Contact\" background_color=\"#2ea3f2\" use_background_color=\"on\" background_layout=\"dark\" text_o