asters-in-community-organizing/\"]\n\nStudy the theory and practice of community organizing in the US context.\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Speaking Tours\" url_new_window=\"off\" animation=\"top\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%149%%\" icon_color=\"#a8a8a8\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle_border=\"on\" circle_border_color=\"#e0e0e0\" icon_placement=\"top\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\n\nDivi will change the way you build websites forever. The advanced page builder makes it possible to build truly dynamic pages without learning code.\n\n[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row admin_label=\"row\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_cta admin_label=\"Call To Action\" title=\"Contact Us\" button_url=\"https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/contact-us-3/\" button_text=\"Contact\" background_color=\"#2ea3f2\" use_background_color=\"on\" background_layout=\"dark\" text_orientation=\"center\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_button=\"off\" button_letter_spacing=\"0\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\"]\n\nHave any questions?\n\n[/et_pb_cta][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]", "Home", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "139-autosave-v1", "", "", "2016-03-23 19:16:10", "2016-03-23 19:16:10", "", "139", "https://projectmexico-premium-rehabescapi.c9users.io/139-autosave-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
